---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About AmperageHQ — who we are and why we created this electrical resource."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 font-heading">About AmperageHQ</h1>

    <p class="text-lg text-text-muted mb-6">
      AmperageHQ is a dedicated resource for electrical professionals and DIY enthusiasts who want accurate, practical information about wiring, electrical codes, and best practices.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 font-heading">Our Mission</h2>
    <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">
      Electricity powers everything we do — and working with it safely requires knowledge, respect, and the right tools. Our mission is to make high-quality electrical information accessible to licensed electricians, apprentices, and homeowners who want to tackle projects safely and correctly.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 font-heading">What We Cover</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-muted space-y-2 mb-6">
      <li>Residential and commercial wiring techniques</li>
      <li>National Electrical Code (NEC) guidance</li>
      <li>Panel upgrades, circuit breakers, and load calculations</li>
      <li>Outlet, switch, and fixture installation</li>
      <li>Electrical safety and arc-fault protection</li>
      <li>Tool reviews and product recommendations</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 font-heading">A Note on Safety</h2>
    <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">
      Electrical work can be dangerous. Always follow your local codes and permit requirements, turn off breakers before working on circuits, and consult a licensed electrician for work that exceeds your skill level or confidence. The information on AmperageHQ is for educational purposes and does not replace professional judgement.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 font-heading">Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
    <p class="text-text-muted">
      AmperageHQ participates in the Amazon Associates program. When you purchase products through links on this site, we may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. This helps us keep the content free and up to date.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
